GameRTP.PaidRespinRTPDescription: The theoretical overall RTP will be reduced when a respin is played on reels that does not lead to any winning result. The theoretical overall RTP will also be reduced due to the rounding effect of the respin cost value (the rounding effect will be lesser at a higher respin cost).
